{
  "stem": "10572.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, he's in camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said bring the friend in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, we want to follow this all the way until we find this guy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we had lots of fun with that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] How long were you with counterintelligence?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of my Army time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until May '46.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I came back to reality and tried to figure out how to make a living.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and ultimately ended up of-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] taking off-- taking on fine menswear lines as a manufacturer's representative, and built a territory over 40 years.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I hope built a reputation for integrity and honesty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I had a following among many of the fine stores in the Midwest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and I'm grateful [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that I have reached this stage in my life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would like to, if I may, end it with a prayer that I wrote for Rosh Hashanah [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] in 1991.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And it says, it was the 9th of November 1938, almost 53 years ago.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "About 75 men of our congregation were led by armed SS around our burning synagogue, our house of worship for 90 years.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A day later, we stood with 11,000 other Jews on the bitter cold windswept mountain they called Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the weeks and months to come, we saw the beast in man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We saw our tormentors and all their cruelties, creatures with human faces but without heart or soul, without the qualities which transform beings in human beings.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were witness to the very beginning of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had no illusions about our future.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Men said their last prayers.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
